OL,6,FGlasgow has introduced a low-emission
OL,7,Fzone (LEZ) to its city centre,
OL,8,Fmeaning drivers of vehicles that do
OL,9,Fnot comply with air pollution
OL,10,Fstandards will face fines.
OL,12,FIt comes into effect on Thursday 1
OL,13,FJune and will be in effect 24 hours a
OL,14,Fday, all year round and is the first
OL,15,Fof four low-emission zones to be
OL,16,Flaunched in Scotland. The penalties
OL,17,Fare harsher than those in existing
OL,18,Flow-emission zones in London and
OL,19,FBirmingham.
